#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:1
msgid ""
"Are you a student willing to participate in WikiToLearn? Awesome! We have "
"thought of some great ways for you to participate. Here are some guidelines "
"that offer you a perspective of what is possible to help you get started:"
msgstr ""
"Sou un estudiant disposat a participar al WikiToLearn? Increïble! Hem pensat "
"en algunes grans maneres perquè hi pugueu participar. Aquí hi ha algunes "
"pautes que us ofereixen una perspectiva del que és possible per ajudar-vos a "
"començar:"

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:3
msgid ""
"Surely you have already got some '''class notes''', though perhaps they are "
"incomplete, poorly organised or not very easy to understand. Why not clean "
"them up a bit and share them on WikiToLearn?"
msgstr ""
"Segurament ja teniu algunes '''notes de classe''', tot i que potser estan "
"incompletes, mal organitzades o no gaire fàcils d'entendre. Per què no "
"netejar-les una mica i compartir-les al WikiToLearn?"

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:5
msgid ""
"Not only will you learn by re-working your notes, but you will then have a "
"convenient, clear and complete text, which will be much much easier for you "
"to study! By collaborating on WikiToLearn, you will be part of a large "
"project creating free texts, in which many other people contribute to the "
"collection of notes, either by submitting new ones or improving existing "
"ones."
msgstr ""
"No només aprendreu mitjançant la reelaboració de les vostres notes, a més "
"disposareu d'un text convenient, clar i complet, que resultarà molt més "
"fàcil per al seu estudi! En col·laborar amb el WikiToLearn, formareu part "
"d'un gran projecte de creació de textos lliures, en el que moltes altres "
"persones contribueixen a la col·lecció de notes, ja sigui publicant-ne de "
"noves o millorant les existents."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:5
msgid "Step 1: Getting started"
msgstr "Pas 1: Com començar"

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:8
msgid ""
"Let's begin with something that you have already done: do you have "
"particularly well written notes that you would like to share?\n"
"If the related course does not yet exist on WikiToLearn, '''[[<ref"
":wikitolearn-guide-chapter-2>|create it]]'''."
msgstr ""
"Anem a començar amb quelcom que ja tingueu fet: Teniu notes particularment "
"ben escrites que us agradaria compartir?\n"
"Si el curs relacionat encara no existeix al WikiToLearn, '''[[<ref"
":wikitolearn-guide-chapter-2>|creeu-lo]]'''."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:8
msgid ""
"If the course already exists, but the specific topics you want to write "
"about are not present, find out how to '''[[<ref:wikitolearn-guide-"
"chapter-3>|add new chapters]]'''."
msgstr ""
"Si el curs ja existeix, però els temes específics sobre els que voleu "
"escriure no estan presents, veieu la manera d''''[[<ref:wikitolearn-guide-"
"chapter-3>|afegir capítols nous]]'''."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:8
msgid ""
"If you want to create concurrent versions of already existing chapters, "
"first evaluate \twhether it would be best just to improve the current "
"version. As a rule of thumb, we try to \tavoid duplicating already written "
"material, but if you believe that you have new suggestions, remember that we "
"enthusiastically support field testing."
msgstr ""
"Si voleu crear versions concurrents de capítols ja existents, en primer lloc "
"avalueu si seria millor només millorar la versió actual. Com a regla "
"general, tractem d'evitar la duplicació de material ja escrit, però si "
"creieu que teniu nous suggeriments, recordeu que nosaltres donem suport amb "
"entusiasme a les proves de camp."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:8
msgid ""
"If you think that everything already exists, and you don't feel like "
"creating something new, simply print all the material you need and start "
"learning from it! There is no better way to help us improve our material "
"than to study from it and give us your feedback."
msgstr ""
"Si penseu que tot ja existeix, i que no teniu ganes de crear alguna cosa "
"nova, només heu d'imprimir tot el material que necessiteu i començar a "
"aprendre d'ell! No hi ha millor manera d'ajudar a millorar el material que "
"no sigui estudiant d'ell i donar-nos la vostra opinió."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:14
msgid ""
"If you have already typed your notes in LaTeX, don't worry, our LaTeX to "
"Wiki converter  is just what you need: learn [[<ref:wikitolearn-guide-"
"chapter-8>|here]] how to import your text!"
msgstr ""
"Si ja heu escrit les vostres notes en LaTeX, no us preocupeu, el nostre "
"convertidor de LaTeX a Wiki és just el que necessiteu: apreneu [[<ref"
":wikitolearn-guide-chapter-8>|aquí]] com importar el vostre text!"

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:16
msgid ""
"If this is the first time you are contributing on WikiToLearn, see the [[<ref"
":wikitolearn-guide-chapter-0>|Manual]]."
msgstr ""
"Si aquesta és la primera vegada que esteu contribuint al WikiToLearn, vegeu "
"el [[<ref:wikitolearn-guide-chapter-0>|Manual]]."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:16
msgid "Step 2: Engage your group"
msgstr "Pas 2: Involucreu al vostre grup"

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:19
msgid ""
"A strategy that we often see working well is to find 3 or 4 friends and form "
"a group with them. You should then split the classes between you according "
"to a set calendar, writing and reviewing the notes in turns. With less than "
"a couple hours per week of work, you will gain a beautiful copy of the "
"lessons, even better than a textbook, and you will optimise the time for "
"your study."
msgstr ""
"Una estratègia que veiem sovint és trobar 3 o 4 amics i formar un grup. A "
"continuació, haureu de dividir les classes entre els usuaris d'acord amb un "
"calendari establert, escriviu i reviseu les notes per torns. Amb menys d'un "
"parell d'hores de treball per setmana, guanyareu una bonica còpia de les "
"classes, fins i tot millor que un llibre de text, i optimitzareu el temps "
"per al vostre estudi."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:19
msgid "Step 3: Spread the word"
msgstr "Pas 3: Difoneu la notícia"

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:22
msgid ""
"There is more! Are you a representative or involved in any student "
"organizations? Talk about WikiToLearn with other students! You would be "
"surprised how many of them would love to use or contribute to something like "
"this."
msgstr ""
"Hi ha més! Sou un representant o participeu en alguna organització "
"d'estudiants? Parleu de WikiToLearn amb altres estudiants! Us sorprendrà de "
"com a molts d'ells els agradaria utilitzar o contribuir d'alguna manera en "
"una cosa com aquesta."

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:24
msgid ""
"Show them how it works and before you know it a local group within your "
"University will kick off. Introduce the project to your professors as well, "
"they can improve and proofread your notes or, who knows, maybe even "
"participate with their own lecture notes!"
msgstr ""
"Mostreu-los com funciona i, abans que us adoneu, s'iniciarà un grup local a "
"la vostra universitat. Presenteu el projecte als professors, d'aquesta "
"manera podran millorar i corregir les vostres notes o, qui sap, potser fins "
"i tot participar amb les seves pròpies!"

#: guide/en/contribute1.txt:26
msgid "With more people involved, everybody gains!"
msgstr "Amb més persones involucrades, tothom hi guanya!"
